<p source="SHANGBO.YANYUANWENYUKONGZI 8.45.1 (STRIP 1) MACHENGYUAN 8: 142 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-1a.1">顏淵問於孔子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-1a.2">“敢問</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-1a.3">君子之內事也有道乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-1a.4">孔子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-1a.5">“有.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-1a.6">顏淵：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-1a.7">“𢽤敢問何如?”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YANYUANWENYUKONGZI 8.45.2 (STRIPS 1, 12A) MACHENGYUAN 8: 142, 155 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-2a.1">孔子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-2a.2">“敬[羞*nu=柔*snu]宥過</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-2a.3">而【1】【先】有司，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-2a.4">老老而慈幼 ，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-2a.5">(豫絞)/(舒繳)而收貧，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-2a.6">祿不足則請，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-2a.7">有餘則辭.【12A】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YANYUANWENYUKONGZI 8.45.3 (STRIPS 2B, 2A, 11) MACHENGYUAN 8: 143, 154 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-3a.1">敬[羞*nu=柔*snu]宥過，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-3a.2">所以爲緩也；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-3a.3">先【2B】【有】司，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-3a.4">所以【2A】𠭁得情；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-3a.5">老老而慈幼，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-3a.6">所以處仁也；</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YANYUANWENYUKONGZI 8.45.4 (STRIPS 11, 12B, 5) MACHENGYUAN 8: 154, 155, 145 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-4a.1">豫絞而收貧，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-4a.2">所以取【11】親也；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-4a.3">祿不足則請，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-4a.4">有餘）【12B】則辭，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-4a.5">所以揚信也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-4a.6">蓋君子之內事也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-4a.7">如此矣.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YANYUANWENYUKONGZI 8.45.5 (STRIPS 5,6) MACHENGYUAN 8: 145-146 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-5a.1">𧧑顏淵曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-5a.2">“君子之內事也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-5a.3">回旣聞命矣，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-5a.4">𢽤敢問【5】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-5a.5">君子之內教也有道乎?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-5a.6">孔子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-5a.7">“有.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-5a.8">顏淵：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-5a.9">“敢問何如?”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YANYUANWENYUKONGZI 8.45.6 (STRIPS 6-7) MACHENGYUAN 8: 146-148 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-6a.1">孔子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-6a.2">“修身以先，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-6a.3">則民莫不從矣；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-6a.4">前【6】以博愛，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-6a.5">則民莫遺親矣；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-6a.6">導之以儉，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-6a.7">則民知足矣；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-6a.8">前之以讓，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-6a.9">則民不爭矣.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YANYUANWENYUKONGZI 8.45.7 (STRIPS 7,9) MACHENGYUAN 8: 148, 151 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-7a.1">或迪而教【7】之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-7a.2">能能，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-7a.3">賤不肖而遠之 ,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-7a.4">則民知禁矣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-7a.5">如進者勸行，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-7a.6">退者知禁，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-7a.7">則其於教也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-7a.8">不遠矣.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YANYUANWENYUKONGZI 8.45.8 (STRIPS 9, 10, 8) MACHENGYUAN 8: 151, 152, 150 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-8a.1">𧧑顏淵曰：【9】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-8a.2">“君子之內教也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-8a.3">回旣聞矣，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-8a.4">敢問至名.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-8a.5">孔子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-8a.6">“德成則名至矣，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-8a.7">名至必卑身，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-8a.8">身治大則〈則大〉祿【10】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YANYUANWENYUKONGZI 8.45.9 (STRIPS 8, 14) MACHENGYUAN 8: 150, 157 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-9a.1">[君子讓]而得之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-9a.2">小人爭而失之.【8】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-9a.3">示則斤，[...] [?]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-9a.4">而毋欲得焉.【14】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YANYUANWENYUKONGZI 8.45.10 (STRIP 13) MACHENGYUAN 8: 156 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-10a.1">屰（素）[遣] 行而信，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-10a.2">先處忠也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-10a.3">貧而安樂，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0074_tls_001-10a.4">先處【13】</seg>
                </p>

</div>
